  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to compeer BHCG levels after Methotrexate ( MTX). treatment for
      Ectopic pregnancy in days 4 and 7 after MTX. to day 10 . The hypothesis is that &quot;BHCG&quot; level
      in day 10 is the best indicator for treatment success , superior to day 4 and 7 . According
      to the investigators impression BHCG level rises in days 4 and 7 due to destruction of the
      trophoblast tissue , and only day 10 is an indicator for treatment success
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
